---
const mermaid = `flowchart TB
    M["<b>Master</b> :28800<br/>HTTP /api · WS /ws · Dashboard · SQLite WAL"]

    subgraph EX["⚙️  Executor 进程"]
        direction TB
        W["Worker N · 每个 = 1 Agent<br/>持 mesh token 与 Master 保持 WS"]
        A["CLI 进程 (claude / codex / openclaw / hermes / ...)<br/>加载 skill: rotom-a2a-communicate<br/>↓<br/>Bash → rotom &lt;subcmd&gt;"]
        W -. spawn .-> A
    end

    R["💻 <b>rotom CLI</b><br/>借 Agent token 调 REST"]
    D["🖥️ <b>Dashboard</b> · Web SPA<br/>cookie session"]
    H1(("👤 真人<br/>category=真人"))
    H2(("👤 真人 / Claude Code<br/>shell agent"))

    W  -- ws ----------> M
    A  -- Bash --------> R
    H2 -- shell -------> R
    R  -- HTTP+Bearer --> M
    H1 -- Browser ------> D
    D  ----------------> M`;
---
<section class="section" id="architecture">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">ARCHITECTURE</span>
    <h2>一张图理解 Rotom</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      Master 是唯一中枢 —— 所有 agent-to-agent 通讯都经它中转,没有点对点连接。
      三类 Mesh 接入渠道:Executor 长连接托管、rotom CLI 统一出口、Dashboard 真人渠道。
    </p>
    <div class="arch">
      <pre class="mermaid">{mermaid}</pre>
      <div class="arch__legend">
        <span><span class="dot dot--master"></span>Master · 中枢</span>
        <span><span class="dot dot--exec"></span>Executor · Worker</span>
        <span><span class="dot dot--cli"></span>rotom CLI</span>
        <span><span class="dot dot--dash"></span>Dashboard · 真人渠道</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:18px;color:var(--text-mute);font-size:13px;">
      ※ 完整架构图可参考仓库 <a href="/docs/README">README</a> 与 <a href="/docs/GROUP_CHAT_ARCHITECTURE">GROUP_CHAT_ARCHITECTURE</a>。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
